arch elf_1
name Fedner the traveler
msg
@match hi
Hello!
I am about to tell my story about the
dark passage.
Would you like to hear?
@match yes
One day I decided to sell my fine
elixers to the denizens of Darkland. I
knew the way would be hard. So I hired
a guide to help me through the dark
passage. We walked through the
passage,then suddenly an arrow flew
from the darkness. My guide pulled out
a crossbow from his pack and I readied
my bow. Then eyes apeared in the
darkness,horrible yellow eyes. The
figure came into the light,it was a
person robbed of his sanity. He carried
a club and growled at us. Then he lept
at us. My guide fired his crossbow and
then,the madman lay dead. We never made
it to the end. My guide was killed by a
dragon. It got out and lived to tell
the story.
endmsg
