arch lesser_dwarven_guard
name Gunther
msg
@match hi|hello
Hey friend!
@match Dark Wood Forest|dark|Dark
Dark Wood Forest is an extremely
dangerous place. Many travelers have
met their grave there. There are many
caves in Dark Wood Forest. But there is
one cave that is filled with treasure.
@match cave
Legend has it,that there was a very
successful bandit who robbed many
dwarves and travelers. His success was
due to his skill at mastering the
magical rites. He stored his treasure
in a cave and summoned 5 xans,5
scorpions,2 panthers,5 spiders,and 2
bats to guard his treasure. The animals
populated the forest and became a
threat to travelers. The bandit soon
died.
@match wood elves|wood elf|Wood elves
The wood elves lived in the Dark Wood
Forest long before the monsters came.
They fashioned magical armour made from
mithril. An art only the dwarves and
the mountain elves mastered. Their bows
shot sure and strong. The wood elves
became in tune with the magic of the
trees.
endmsg
